Package: ggpatina
Type: Package
Title: Period Aesthetics and Analog Aging Effects for ggplot
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Prybylski", , "jprybylski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5802-0539"))
Description: Apply period-inspired fonts and analog-aging visual effects to ggplot figures. 
    Includes presets for transparency slide and old-journal scan looks, plus ink bleed,
    Kodachrome-style fade, photocopy misalignment, and a blueprint (cyanotype) style.
